at starts the server writes into `servers` on [this line](https://github.com/amuttsch/goswagger-race/blob/master/restapi/server.go#L190). Before it starts a goroutine to handle shutdowns [here](https://github.com/amuttsch/goswagger-race/blob/master/restapi/server.go#L178). In the `handleShutdown()` method `servers` is accessed again which causes a data race:\r\n\r\n```\r\n==================\r\nWARNING: DATA RACE\r\nRead at 0x00c0000ac180 by goroutine 27:\r\n  goswagger-race/restapi.(*Server).handleShutdown()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/restapi/server.go:418 +0xba\r\n\r\nPrevious write at 0x00c0000ac180 by main goroutine:\r\n  goswagger-race/restapi.(*Server).Serve()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/restapi/server.go:220 +0x1b5a\r\n  main.main()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/cmd/example-server/main.go:60 +0x64a\r\n\r\nGoroutine 27 (running) created at:\r\n  goswagger-race/restapi.(*Server).Serve()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/restapi/server.go:178 +0x26e\r\n  main.main()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/cmd/example-server/main.go:60 +0x64a\r\n==================\r\n==================\r\nWARNING: DATA RACE\r\nRead at 0x00c0004ce010 by goroutine 27:\r\n  goswagger-race/restapi.(*Server).handleShutdown()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/restapi/server.go:425 +0x1a6\r\n\r\nPrevious write at 0x00c0004ce010 by main goroutine:\r\n  goswagger-race/restapi.(*Server).Serve()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/restapi/server.go:220 +0x1b20\r\n  main.main()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/cmd/example-server/main.go:60 +0x64a\r\n\r\nGoroutine 27 (running) created at:\r\n  goswagger-race/restapi.(*Server).Serve()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/restapi/server.go:178 +0x26e\r\n  main.main()\r\n      .../goswagger-race/cmd/example-server/main.go:60 +0x64a\r\n==================\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Swagger specification\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/amuttsch/goswagger-race/blob/master/swagger.yaml\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nTo reproduce clone my repo https://github.com/amuttsch/goswagger-race , run `go run -race cmd/example-server/main.go` and wait a few seconds.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\nswagger version: 0.19.0\r\ngo version: 1.12\r\nOS: Linux\r\n\r\nRelated to #1781 ","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-swagger/go-swagger/issues/1943/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-swagger/go-swagger/issues/1943/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"}]